This is how to count_up_to of n:
   Remember that result is []
   Remember that x is 2
   Do this diff of n and 1 times:
      Remember that prime is 1
      Remember that d is 2
      Do this diff of x and 2 times:
         When remainder of x and d is 0, then:
            Remember that prime is 0
         End when
         Increase d
      End do
      When prime is 1, then:
         Add result to x
      End when
      Increase x
   End do
   The answer is result
